      • getPwMockLocationProvider

        public final PwLocationProvider getPwMockLocationProvider(android.content.Context context,
                                                          String jsonFileName,
                                                          PwMockLocationProvider.MockLocationsDisabledListener listener,
                                                          boolean repeat)
        Creates a PwMock LocationProvider
        Parameters:
        context - The application context object
        jsonFileName - The name and path of the json file to be used for location data. Starting after "assets/"
        listener - The listener to be notified when the application determines that the user has mock locations disabled. If null, no location and no user feedback will be shown.
        repeat - True if you wish to repeat the mock locations indefinitely
        Returns:
        Instance of PwMock LocationProvider
